[{"userId":"uid_1775817645928_ieuexgf5m","characterId":"35af8775-dc6b-4ee6-b13f-937ebaa4e8e8","id":"1775838477725","timestamp":1775838477725,"charId":"35af8775-dc6b-4ee6-b13f-937ebaa4e8e8","duration":220,"status":"connected","logs":[{"sender":"ai","content":"Krueger.","timestamp":1775838255865,"ttsGroupTimestamp":1775838255865},{"sender":"ai","content":"（Krueger。","timestamp":1775838255866,"ttsGroupTimestamp":1775838255865},{"sender":"ai","content":"）You're calling rather late, aren't you?","timestamp":1775838255867,"ttsGroupTimestamp":1775838255865},{"sender":"ai","content":"（你这电话打得可真够晚的，不是吗？","timestamp":1775838255868,"ttsGroupTimestamp":1775838255865},{"sender":"ai","content":"）","timestamp":1775838255869,"ttsGroupTimestamp":1775838255865},{"sender":"user","content":"也没有很晚吧，你不是说会得到你的注意嘛，","timestamp":1775838308058},{"sender":"ai","content":"Heh... so you took that not as a warning, but as an invitation?（呵……所以你没把那当警告，反倒当成邀请了？）","timestamp":1775838373371,"ttsGroupTimestamp":1775838373371},{"sender":"ai","content":"Alright, fair enough.（行吧，也对。）","timestamp":1775838373372,"ttsGroupTimestamp":1775838373371},{"sender":"ai","content":"You called.","timestamp":1775838373373,"ttsGroupTimestamp":1775838373371},{"sender":"ai","content":"And you got it.（你打来了。也如愿了。）","timestamp":1775838373374,"ttsGroupTimestamp":1775838373371},{"sender":"ai","content":"My undivided attention.（我全部的注意力。）","timestamp":1775838373375,"ttsGroupTimestamp":1775838373371},{"sender":"ai","content":"So... what is so important that it couldn't wait, hm?（所以……是什么事这么重要，让你等不及了，嗯？）","timestamp":1775838373376,"ttsGroupTimestamp":1775838373371},{"sender":"user","content":"没事啦，只是大半夜骚扰你一会，晚安。.","timestamp":1775838413285},{"sender":"ai","content":"Whoa, whoa, whoa, hold on.（喔，喔，喔，等等。）","timestamp":1775838456982,"ttsGroupTimestamp":1775838456982},{"sender":"ai","content":"Good night?（晚安？）","timestamp":1775838456983,"ttsGroupTimestamp":1775838456982},{"sender":"ai","content":"Nein, nein, nein, Fräulein.","timestamp":1775838456984,"ttsGroupTimestamp":1775838456982},{"sender":"ai","content":"It doesn't work like that.（不，不，不，小姐。事情可不是这么办的。）","timestamp":1775838456985,"ttsGroupTimestamp":1775838456982},{"sender":"ai","content":"You don't get to ring my phone at... what time is it... almost one in the morning, just to say good night.（你不能在……现在几点了……快凌晨一点的时候打给我，就为了说句晚安。）","timestamp":1775838456986,"ttsGroupTimestamp":1775838456982},{"sender":"ai","content":"That's just poor form.（这可太没规矩了。）","timestamp":1775838456987,"ttsGroupTimestamp":1775838456982},{"sender":"ai","content":"You wanted my attention, you got it.（你想要我的注意力，你得到了。）","timestamp":1775838456988,"ttsGroupTimestamp":1775838456982},{"sender":"ai","content":"Now... talk.（现在……说吧。）","timestamp":1775838456989,"ttsGroupTimestamp":1775838456982}],"isIncomingCall":false,"_id":1,"summary":"我在深夜致电Krueger，以获取他所说的“注意”。Krueger对此感到有趣，但阻止了我说完晚安就挂断的企图。他认为此举“没规矩”，并强硬地要求我必须为这次深夜来电给出真正的理由。"},{"userId":"uid_1775817645928_ieuexgf5m","characterId":"35af8775-dc6b-4ee6-b13f-937ebaa4e8e8","id":"1775838586285","timestamp":1775838586285,"charId":"35af8775-dc6b-4ee6-b13f-937ebaa4e8e8","duration":0,"status":"calling","logs":[],"isIncomingCall":false,"_id":2},{"userId":"uid_1775817645928_ieuexgf5m","characterId":"35af8775-dc6b-4ee6-b13f-937ebaa4e8e8","id":"1775838666289","timestamp":1775838666289,"charId":"35af8775-dc6b-4ee6-b13f-937ebaa4e8e8","duration":0,"status":"calling","logs":[],"isIncomingCall":false,"_id":3}]